## ChatSim Template

The ChatSim template — including all UI systems, scene structure, save system,
and supporting code outside of the BubbleSpinner module — is free to use for
personal and commercial projects.

You are free to:
- Use this template to build and ship your own games, including commercial releases
- Modify it to suit your project
- Build and sell games made with it

You may NOT:
- Resell or redistribute this template as-is
- Repackage it as an asset pack, starter kit, boilerplate, or tool for others
- Claim it as your own original work

