## BubbleSpinner Dialogue Engine

The BubbleSpinner module — including the parser, executor, conversation manager,
data structures, and related files under Assets/Scripts/BubbleSpinner/ — is free
to use in your own projects, including commercial games.

You are free to:
- Use BubbleSpinner in personal and commercial projects
- Modify it as needed for your game

You may NOT:
- Redistribute BubbleSpinner in any form as a standalone tool, plugin, or package
- Include BubbleSpinner in any asset pack, template, or toolkit distributed to others
- Resell or repackage BubbleSpinner in any form intended for developers
- Claim authorship of BubbleSpinner

Note:
Redistribution as part of a compiled game build is allowed.

